column3: Database:
column6:
SELECT

SR.SchemeRangeName AS [Range]
,SD.PortfolioLongName AS [Fund]
,ssc.Share_Class_Name_Long AS [ShareClass]
,SP.PriceDate
,SP.QuotedBid

FROM Schemes.SchemePrices SP 
JOIN Schemes.ShareClasses ssc ON ssc.ShareClassID = SP.ShareClassID
JOIN Schemes.SchemeDetails SD ON SD.pID = ssc.pID
JOIN Schemes.SchemeRange SR ON SR.SchemeRangeID = SD.SchemeRangeID
WHERE SD.SchemeRangeID IN (1)
AND SP.PriceDate BETWEEN '2015-06-01' AND '2022-09-30'
ORDER BY SP.PriceDate, SR.SchemeRangeName, SD.PortfolioLongName, ssc.Share_Class_Name_Long
